ORDER WITH CONFIDENCE – FREE RETURNS AND FULL MONEY BACK GUARANTEE!

We aim to dispatch all orders within 3 business days.

EIRE/EUROPE/REST OF THE WORLD – WE SHIP WORLDWIDE!

Please note we ship safely worldwide so please order with confidence. Dispatch details are the same as UK but please allow a little extra time for delivery. Please order with confidence as we offer a full free no quibble returns policy (Subject to our normal terms and conditions – see here).

POSTAGE AND PACKING RATES:

UK: $5.99 per order (free for orders over $112.99)

All standard UK orders are tracked upon dispatch.

For an urgent order, why not try...

UK – Next Day Delivery: $9.99 per order

If you need your order in a hurry we offer a next day service by courier to mainland Britain. The order cut off for this service is 2PM. All orders placed on a Friday after 2PM (or Thursday if Friday is a Bank Holiday) will be delivered the following Tuesday (Wednesday if there is a Bank Holiday Monday). Please note that no deliveries are made on UK Bank Holidays. This service is also available to the Channel Islands, Northern Ireland, Isle of Wight, Isle of Man and the Scottish Highlands; however your order may take an extra day to be delivered to these destinations.

EUROPE & THE REST OF THE WORLD:

International Tracked: $13.99 per order up to $56.99, $16.99 per order between $56.99 & $112.99, then an additional $5.99 per $56.99 extra spent (Secure Delivery Service)

PLEASE NOTE: In some European countries you may be asked to pay a surcharge to receive your parcel.

For delivery enquiries please call 0330 043 2441.
